summary: PASSENGER AIRBAG DEACTIVATES WHILE A PASSENGER IS IN THE SEAT. IT HAPPENS INTERMITTENTLY. THERE ARE NO ELECTRONICS PLUGGED INTO MY CAR. THIS HAS BEEN HAPPENING SINCE I PURCHASED THE CAR IN 2014. MY CAR IS STILL UNDER WARRANTY AND THERE DOES NOT SEEM TO BE A RESOLUTION IN SIGHT/ MY CAR IS IN THE SHOP RIGHT NOW AND THEY ARE TELLING ME MY CAR IS WORKING AS DESIGNED.
